  "description": "A modifier is a numerical bonus or penalty applied to a dice roll in a [tabletop role-playing game](../_index.md). Modifiers represent the influence of a [character's](../../../terms/character.md) abilities, circumstances, equipment, or other factors on the probability of success.",
